Our response times are down 75% and customer satisfaction is up 50%.", name: "Sarah Chen", role: "Customer Success Manager at TechCorp" }, { content: "The lead generation AI is incredible. It's like having a full-time sales team working 24/7. Our qualified leads have increased by 300%.", name: "Michael Rodriguez", role: "Sales Director at GrowthCo" }, { content: "Employee onboarding used to take weeks of our HR team's time.
